files.docstring:
Manage .env configuration for LLM provider settings.

Reads/writes the project .env file. Only manages LLM-related keys;
preserves all other entries (Dify credentials, etc.) untouched.

functions.docstring:
从 context 中按路径段逐级取值。

context 结构:
  {
    "params": {"ts_code": "600519.SH", ...},
    "stages": {
        "download": {"step2_ac": {"json_output": "..."}, ...},
        "snapshot": {"json_output": "..."},
    },
    "loop_count": 2,  # 循环计数器
  }

解析 stage.map 中的所有值引用，返回实际值 dict。

mapping: {"ts_code": "$params.ts_code", "ac_json": "$download.step2_ac.json_output"}
返回:    {"ts_code": "600519.SH", "ac_json": "..."}

非 $ 开头的值视为字面量直接保留。

